  "description": "VS Code / Cursor-inspired live developer dashboard for Wallpaper Engine. Features a live clock, detailed real-time weather, terminal command cheatsheet, Windows hotkeys reference, and data-driven language lessons (Thai, Spanish, English, Russian, Japanese, Korean). Multi-language interface (EN/RU/ES/JA/KO/TH) with separate primary and study language, quick-access app board, custom module/text colors, tri-state backgrounds and duplicable widgets. A numbers/counting module, renamable & duplicable widgets. Fully customizable themes and drag & resize layout. v1.2.",
